title: Links to windows builds in os setup documentation are bad
body_html:
Build location is listed under https://www.tensorflow.org/versions/r0.12/get_started/os_setup.html#pip-installation-on-windows

For example when trying to retrieve:

https://storage.googleapis.com/tensorflow/windows/cpu/tensorflow-0.12.0rc1-cp35-cp35m-win_amd64.whl

I get the response

<Error>
   <Code>NoSuchKey</Code>
   <Message>The specified key does not exist.</Message>
</Error>
